title: Gutjahr called up to U20 national team
text:
Gutjahr called up to U20 national team Jeremy Price, The Hoosier Scoop heraldtimesonline.com | 0 comments 
Bloomington North grad and Indiana University freshman soccer player Jeremiah Gutjahr will take a leave from the Hoosiers to join the United States U20 national team in Germany this week and next. Here’s the full release from IU:
